query:
-- Get order details
SELECT id, userId, status, processedSkus, totalSkus, zipFileUrl, createdAt, completedAt 
FROM orders 
WHERE id = 420003;

-- Get order items
SELECT id, orderId, sku, status, imagesFound, errorMessage 
FROM orderItems 
WHERE orderId = 420003;

-- Get scraped images for this order
SELECT id, orderItemId, imageUrl, source, resolution, fileSize 
FROM scrapedImages 
WHERE orderItemId IN (SELECT id FROM orderItems WHERE orderId = 420003);
